# CEE — Holding Inbox
# Async GTD holding area for tasks not immediately actionable.
# PURGE RULE: Any item older than 30 days without user request is deleted at weekly audit.
# LOCATION: context/ — same register as tasks.md and para-projects.md (active working state)
# This file is GITIGNORED.
