---

## Processing Rules (applied by CEE Triage Agent)

```
On each item entering this inbox:
  1. Is it actionable under a Core Objective or Role?
     → NO  : Move to semantic/para-resources.md or memory/archive/para-archive.md
     → YES : Can it be automated (Termite)?
              → YES: Execute in session, log in memory/logs/termite-history.md
              → NO : Requires user intervention?
                     → YES: Append to Today's Top 3 (briefing alert)
                     → NO : Stay in Holding Inbox until weekly audit
```

